-- China NDRC Approves Beiqi Foton Venture With Daimler, Business News Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-14T23:10:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/china-ndrc-approves-beiqi-foton-venture-with-daimler-business-news-says.html

          
          
             China’s National Development and
Reform Commission has given approval for Beiqi Foton Motor Co.’s
planned venture with Daimler AG to produce commercial vehicles,
China Business News reported today, citing an unidentified
person at the Chinese carmaker.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
